HEADWORD: Interspiration
<hw>In`ter*spi*ra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>interspiratio</ets>. See <er>Inter-</er>, and
<er>Spirit</er>.]</ety> <def>Spiritual inspiration at separate times, or
